Spare hashpower is converted into:

\begin{itemize}
    \item weakwork claims,
    \item short-horizon priority,
    \item admission or routing rights,
    \item saleable provider-side utility.
\end{itemize}

\subsection{Patience to Coordination}

Spare patience is converted into:

\begin{itemize}
    \item HODL-derived privilege,
    \item long-horizon participation rights,
